  "title": "Smart Disconnect",
  "description": "It allows easy monitoring of player status, and ensures smooth gameplay by letting AI take over when a player disconnects. When a player reconnects, they seamlessly resume control of their previous character.",
  "longDescription": "<p>SmartDisconnect is a streamlined tool for managing player connections in multiplayer games. It allows easy monitoring of player status, and ensures smooth gameplay by letting AI take over when a player disconnects. When a player reconnects, they seamlessly resume control of their previous character. The asset also efficiently handles player names, is easy to use, and optimized for performance.</p><p><br /></p><p>Video Presentation:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v&#61;s8OHUxbKXk0\" rel=\"nofollow\"> &gt;&gt;&gt; HERE &lt;&lt;&lt;</a></p><p>Support (Discord): <a href=\"https://discord.gg/kXQ2KsZkrd\" rel=\"nofollow\">&gt;&gt;&gt; HERE &lt;&lt;&lt;</a></p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1c5xbps7bjUHpT6NxUP-qhyocqC6F_pgo/view?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">&gt;&gt;&gt; HERE &lt;&lt;&lt;</a></p><p><br /></p><p>&#x1f4e3;Check other systems: &gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/profile/Risecode?count&#61;20&amp;sortBy&#61;effectiveDate&amp;sortDir&#61;DESC&amp;start&#61;0&amp;tag&#61;11\" rel=\"nofollow\">HERE</a>&lt;&lt;&lt;</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Free plugin required:</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/safe-pawn\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>SafePawn</strong> </a>[5.2&#43;] <strong>(without a plugin, it will only work when the player exits the game themselves)</strong></li></ul>",
  "technicalDetails": "<h4><strong>✅Features:</strong></h4><p><br /></p><ul><li>Server browser, host</li><li>Player status</li><li>When a player disconnects, AI takes over control</li><li>When a player reconnects, they will take over the character they were playing before disconnecting</li><li>Player name</li><li>Easy to use</li><li>Optimized</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 22</p><p>Input: (Mouse)</p><p>Network Replicated: Yes</p><p>Supported Development Platforms:</p><p>Windows: Yes</p><p>Mac: Not Tested</p><p><br /></p>",
